HOUSE RESOLUTION NO. 281
BY REPRESENTATIVE CHASSION
SPECIAL DAY/WEEK/MONTH: Designates May 14, 2026, as Community Action Day
in Louisiana
1 A RESOLUTION
2 To designate Thursday, May 14, 2026, as Community Action Day in Louisiana and to
3 commend the Association of Community Action Partnerships Louisiana (ACAP-LA)
4 for its efforts to address poverty in the state.
5 WHEREAS, the mission of ACAP-LA is to ensure that the causes and conditions of
6 poverty are effectively addressed and to strengthen, promote, represent, and serve the
7 community action network; and
8 WHEREAS, ACAP-LA changes people's lives, embodies the spirit of hope, improves
9 communities, and makes the United States a better place to live; the organization cares about
10 the entire community and is dedicated to helping people help themselves and each other; and
11 WHEREAS, representatives of the forty-two ACAP-LA agencies across the state will
12 gather at the state capitol to commemorate May as National Community Action Month in
13 honor of the millions of Americans who have been impacted by human, health, and social
14 services.
15 THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the House of Representatives of the
16 Legislature of Louisiana does hereby designate Thursday, May 14, 2026, as Community
17 Action Day in Louisiana and does hereby commend the Association of Community Action
18 Partnerships Louisiana for its efforts to address poverty in the state.
